{"tid":849264,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[創先河] 金融時報說從試過記者在香港不獲續發工作簽證","createTime":"2018-10-05T14:23:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-07T15:47:19.000Z","uid":141151,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"50d3cf81275b48fbbf30dd8bb6eef61504bdf696","tid":849264,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T14:23:26.000Z","msg":"金融時報說從試過記者在香港不獲續發工作簽證<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsId=20181005183615\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Flive.aspx%3FNewsId%3D20181005183615&d=LVeiHdKwMKcZ54QT6wQ44TPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=00a85cbf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsId=20181005183615</a><br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;香港外國記者會其中一位副主席, 在《金融時報》任職亞洲新聞編輯的馬凱Victor Mallet, 被拒續發工作簽證, 港府並沒解釋原因.<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;報道引述《金融時報》發言人說, 今次是《金融時報》首次在香港遇到的情況.<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;馬凱主持民族黨召集人陳浩天在外國記者會的午餐會演講. 民主黨立法會議員涂謹申指, 事件難免令人質疑當局, 今次是向外國記者會報復. 曾任記者的議會陣線毛孟靜就說, 記憶中從未試過有外國記者, 不獲續發工作簽證, 認為事件開壞先例, 定必影響香港新聞自由的排名度.<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;經民聯梁美芬就說, 外交部先後兩次發聲明, 譴責外國記者會設平台讓陳浩天宣揚港獨, 反映事件已超越一國兩制範圍, 並非香港能處理的事務. 梁美芬認為今次個案帶出清楚信息, 任何人都不應舉辦類似的平台宣揚港獨.<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;"},{"pid":"11797b83432df7b7ac398d23e6618d06750f27fb","tid":849264,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T14:24:47.000Z","msg":"Financial Times 都得罪真係嫌命長<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://martinoei.com/article/21823/financial-times-%e9%83%bd%e5%be%97%e7%bd%aa%e7%9c%9f%e4%bf%82%e5%ab%8c%e5%91%bd%e9%95%b7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmartinoei.com%2Farticle%2F21823%2Ffinancial-times-%25e9%2583%25bd%25e5%25be%2597%25e7%25bd%25aa%25e7%259c%259f%25e4%25bf%2582%25e5%25ab%258c%25e5%2591%25bd%25e9